name: MARVEL ENDGAME: PART I - THE TIME HEIST & PART II - THE FINAL STAND
description:
Some people move on. But not us.

To celebrate the 10th anniversary of Disney Infinity 3.0, we present the first chapter of the biggest and most ambitious Toybox collaboration ever attempted: Marvel Avengers: Endgame.

Part I throws you into a universe reeling from despair. Five years after the Decimation, a single spark of hope emerges. Your mission: join the remaining Avengers on a desperate Time Heist to retrieve the Infinity Stones. Journey through time and space to the besieged New York of 2012, the majestic halls of Asgard, the desolate plains of Morag, and the heartbreaking cliffs of Vormir.

The fate of all existence rests on your shoulders. Assemble your team. Get the stones. But be warned: changing the past is only half the battle. The conclusion... is coming.

"Avengers... Assemble."

This is it. The epic conclusion to the Disney Infinity Endgame saga is here. The Time Heist was a success, but the war is far from over.

Part II begins at the exact moment hope is restored‚Äîand immediately unleashes the final, cataclysmic battle for the fate of the universe. Witness the reversal of the Snap and face a new Thanos, angrier and more determined than ever.

This is a conflict so massive it could not be contained in a single Toybox. Prepare for a three-part final battle that recreates the entire climax of the film. Will you be worthy? Can you withstand the onslaught? This is the last stand. The fight of your lives.

Whatever it takes.

A Toybox by: Infiniteer Adventures x LiontHD x The Bow-Tie Guy x Poppa H x 72Pringle & ThatBrownBat.
